```{r pancreas 32828686, include=FALSE}

PMID_32828686 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32828686', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32828686 <- paste0(PMID_32828686$journal,' ', PMID_32828686$year, ' ', PMID_32828686$month,';', PMID_32828686$volume,'(', PMID_32828686$number,'):', PMID_32828686$pages)

PubMed_32828686 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32828686$eprint)

doi_32828686 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32828686$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
